TranslatedText: 通过代理服务器进行身份验证失败。

OriginalText: The connection to the server timed out.
The page contains too many server redirects.
TranslatedText: 该页面包含太多服务器重定向。

OriginalText: Too many requests are being processed. Try again later.
TranslatedText: 正在处理的请求太多，请稍后重试。

OriginalText: Phone storage is full. Delete some files to free space.
TranslatedText: 手机存储空间已满。请删除一些文件以腾出空间。

OriginalText: Do you want to shut down?

TranslatedText: 重新启动并进入安全模式

OriginalText: Do you want to reboot into safe mode? This will disable all third party applications you have installed. They will be restored when you reboot again.
TranslatedText: 您要重新启动并进入安全模式吗？这样会停用您已安装的所有第三方应用。再次重新启动将恢复这些应用。
最近没有运行任何应用

OriginalText: Do things that can cost you money.
TranslatedText: 执行可能需要您付费的操作。

OriginalText: Read and write your SMS, email, and other messages.
TranslatedText: 读写短信、电子邮件和其他消息。

OriginalText: Direct access to your contacts and calendar stored on the phone.
TranslatedText: 直接访问手机上存储的联系人和日历。

OriginalText: Direct access to hardware on the handset.
TranslatedText: 直接访问手机上的硬件。

OriginalText: Monitor, record, and process phone calls.
TranslatedText: 监管、记录和处理电话呼叫。

OriginalText: Lower-level access and control of the system.
TranslatedText: 对系统进行低级访问和控制。

OriginalText: Features only needed for app developers.
TranslatedText: 只有应用开发者才需要的功能。

OriginalText: Allows the app to disable the status bar or add and remove system icons.
TranslatedText: 允许应用停用状态栏或者增删系统图标。

OriginalText: Allows the app to be the status bar.
TranslatedText: 允许以状态栏形式显示应用。

OriginalText: Allows the app to expand or collapse the status bar.
TranslatedText: 允许应用展开或折叠状态栏。
重新设置外拨电话的路径

OriginalText: Allows the app to process outgoing calls and change the number to be dialed. This permission allows the app to monitor, redirect, or prevent outgoing calls.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用处理外拨电话以及更改要拨打的号码。此权限可让该应用监视、重定向或阻止外拨电话。

OriginalText: Allows the app to receive and process SMS messages. This means the app could monitor or delete messages sent to your device without showing them to you.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用接收和处理短信。这就意味着，该应用可能会监视发送到您设备的短信，或删除发送到您设备的短信而不向您显示。

OriginalText: Allows the app to receive and process MMS messages. This means the app could monitor or delete messages sent to your device without showing them to you.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用接收和处理彩信。这就意味着，该应用可能会监视发送到您设备的彩信，或删除发送到您设备的彩信而不向您显示。

OriginalText: Allows the app to receive and process emergency broadcast messages. This permission is only available to system apps.
TranslatedText: 允许应用接收和处理紧急广播消息。此权限仅适用于系统应用。

OriginalText: Allows the app to read cell broadcast messages received by your device. Cell broadcast alerts are delivered in some locations to warn you of emergency situations. Malicious apps may interfere with the performance or operation of your device when an emergency cell broadcast is received.
TranslatedText: 允许应用读取您的设备收到的小区广播消息。小区广播消息是在某些地区发送的、用于发布紧急情况警告的提醒信息。恶意应用可能会在您收到小区紧急广播时干扰您设备的性能或操作。

OriginalText: Allows the app to send SMS messages. This may result in unexpected charges. Malicious apps may cost you money by sending messages without your confirmation.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用发送短信。此权限可能会导致意外收费。恶意应用可能会未经您的确认而发送短信，由此产生相关费用。

OriginalText: send SMS messages with no confirmation
TranslatedText: 不经确认直接发送短信

OriginalText: Allows the app to send SMS messages. This may result in unexpected charges. Malicious apps may cost you money by sending messages without your confirmation.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用发送短信。此权限可能会导致意外收费。恶意应用可能会未经您的确认而发送短信，由此产生相关费用。

OriginalText: read your text messages (SMS or MMS)
TranslatedText: 读取您的文字讯息（短信或彩信）

OriginalText: Allows the app to read SMS messages stored on your phone or SIM card. This allows the app to read all SMS messages, regardless of content or confidentiality.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用读取您手机或 SIM 卡上存储的短信。此权限可让该应用读取所有短信，而不考虑短信内容或机密性。

OriginalText: edit your text messages (SMS or MMS)
TranslatedText: 编辑您的文字讯息（短信或彩信）

OriginalText: Allows the app to write to SMS messages stored on your phone or SIM card. Malicious apps may delete your messages.
TranslatedText: 允许应用对手机或 SIM 卡上存储的短信执行写入操作。恶意应用可能会删除您的短信。

OriginalText: Allows the app to receive and process WAP messages. This permission includes the ability to monitor or delete messages sent to you without showing them to you.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用接收和处理 WAP 消息。此权限包括监视发送给您的消息或删除发送给您的消息而不向您显示的功能。

OriginalText: Allows the app to retrieve information about currently and recently running tasks. This may allow the app to discover information about which applications are used on the device.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用检索近期运行的和当前正在运行的任务的相关信息。此权限可让该应用了解设备上使用了哪些应用。
检索正在运行的应用的详细信息

OriginalText: Allows the app to retrieve detailed information about currently and recently running tasks. Malicious apps may discover private information about other apps.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用检索当前正在运行和近期运行的任务的详细信息。恶意应用可能会发现有关其他应用的私密信息。
对正在运行的应用重新排序

OriginalText: Allows the app to move tasks to the foreground and background. The app may do this without your input.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用将任务移动到前台和后台。该应用可能不经您的命令自行执行此操作。

OriginalText: Allows the app to remove tasks and kill their apps. Malicious apps may disrupt the behavior of other apps.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用删除任务并终止这些任务的应用。恶意应用可以籍此影响其他应用的行为。

OriginalText: Allows the app to start any activity, regardless of permission protection or exported state.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用启动任何活动（不考虑权限保护或导出状态）。

OriginalText: Allows the app to control the screen compatibility mode of other applications. Malicious applications may break the behavior of other applications.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用控制其他应用的屏幕兼容模式。恶意应用可以籍此影响其他应用的行为。

OriginalText: Allows the app to turn on debugging for another app. Malicious apps may use this to kill other apps.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用对其他应用启用调试。恶意应用可以籍此终止其他的应用。

OriginalText: Allows the app to change the current configuration, such as the locale or overall font size.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用更改当前配置，例如语言区域或整体的字体大小。

OriginalText: Allows the app to enable the car mode.
TranslatedText: 允许应用启用车载模式。

OriginalText: Allows the app to end background processes of other apps. This may cause other apps to stop running.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用结束其他应用的后台进程。此权限可导致其他应用停止运行。

OriginalText: Allows the app to forcibly stop other apps.
TranslatedText: 允许应用强行停止其他应用。

OriginalText: Allows the app to force any activity that is in the foreground to close and go back. Should never be needed for normal apps.
TranslatedText: 允许应用强制关闭任何前台活动并返回。普通应用绝不需要此权限。

OriginalText: Allows the app to retrieve internal state of the system. Malicious apps may retrieve a wide variety of private and secure information that they should never normally need.
TranslatedText: 允许应用检索系统的内部状态。恶意应用可能会检索一般情况下绝不需要检索的多种私人信息和安全信息。

OriginalText: Allows the app to retrieve the content of the active window. Malicious apps may retrieve the entire window content and examine all its text except passwords.
TranslatedText: 允许应用检索活动窗口的内容。恶意应用可能会检索整个窗口的内容，并检查其中除密码以外的所有文字。

OriginalText: Puts the activity manager into a shutdown state. Does not perform a complete shutdown.
TranslatedText: 使活动管理器进入关闭状态。不执行彻底关机。

OriginalText: Prevents the user from switching to another app.
TranslatedText: 阻止用户切换到其他应用。

OriginalText: monitor and control all app launching
Allows the app to monitor and control how the system launches activities. Malicious apps may completely compromise the system. This permission is only needed for development, never for normal use.
TranslatedText: 允许应用监视和控制系统是如何启动活动的。恶意应用可能会完全破坏系统。此权限只有在进行开发时才需要，正常使用情况下绝不需要。

OriginalText: Allows the app to broadcast a notification that an app package has been removed. Malicious apps may use this to kill any other running app.
TranslatedText: 允许应用广播一条有关已删除了应用包的通知。恶意应用可能借此终止其他任何正在运行的应用。

OriginalText: Allows the app to broadcast a notification that an SMS message has been received. Malicious apps may use this to forge incoming SMS messages.
TranslatedText: 允许应用广播一条有关已收到短信的通知。恶意应用可能借此伪造接到的短信。
发送 WAP-PUSH 收到的广播

OriginalText: Allows the app to broadcast a notification that a WAP PUSH message has been received. Malicious apps may use this to forge MMS message receipt or to silently replace the content of any webpage with malicious variants.
TranslatedText: 允许应用广播一条有关已收到 WAP PUSH 短信的通知。恶意应用可能借此伪造短信接收，或在后台将任意网页的内容替换为恶意内容。

OriginalText: Allows the app to control the maximum number of processes that will run. Never needed for normal apps.
TranslatedText: 允许应用控制将运行的进程数上限。普通应用绝不需要此权限。

OriginalText: Allows the app to control whether activities are always finished as soon as they go to the background. Never needed for normal apps.
TranslatedText: 允许应用控制活动在转入后台后是否立即结束。普通应用绝不需要此权限。

OriginalText: Allows the app to modify collected battery statistics. Not for use by normal apps.
TranslatedText: 允许应用修改收集到的电池统计信息。普通应用不能使用此权限。

OriginalText: Allows the app to control the system's backup and restore mechanism. Not for use by normal apps.""
TranslatedText: 允许应用控制系统的备份和还原机制。普通应用不能使用此权限。

OriginalText: confirm a full backup or restore operation
TranslatedText: 确认完整备份或恢复操作

OriginalText: Allows the app to launch the full backup confirmation UI. Not to be used by any app.
TranslatedText: 允许应用启动完整备份确认用户界面。不用于任何应用。

OriginalText: Allows the app to create windows that are intended to be used by the internal system user interface. Not for use by normal apps.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用创建供内部系统用户界面使用的窗口。普通应用不应使用此权限。
在其他应用之上显示内容

OriginalText: Allows the app to show system alert windows. Some alert windows may take over the entire screen.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用显示系统提醒窗口。某些提醒窗口可能会占据整个屏幕。

OriginalText: Allows the app to change the global animation speed (faster or slower animations) at any time.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用随时更改全局动画速度（加快或减慢）。

OriginalText: Allows the app to create and manage their own tokens, bypassing their normal Z-ordering. Should never be needed for normal apps.
TranslatedText: 允许应用绕过其正常的 Z 排序创建和管理自己的令牌。普通应用绝不需要此权限。

OriginalText: Allows the app to deliver its own input events (key presses, etc.) to other apps. Malicious apps may use this to take over the phone.
TranslatedText: 允许应用将自身的输入活动（例如按键操作等）提供给其他应用。恶意应用可能借此控制手机。

OriginalText: record what you type and actions you take
TranslatedText: 记录您键入的内容和执行的操作

OriginalText: Allows the app to watch the keys you press even when interacting with another app (such as typing a password). Should never be needed for normal apps.
TranslatedText: 允许应用记录您所按的键，包括与其他应用进行交互（如输入密码）时按的键。普通应用绝不需要此权限。

OriginalText: Allows the holder to bind to the top-level interface of an input method. Should never be needed for normal apps.
TranslatedText: 允许用户绑定至输入法的顶级接口。普通应用绝不需要此权限。

OriginalText: Allows the holder to bind to the top-level interface of an accessibility service. Should never be needed for normal apps.
TranslatedText: 允许应用绑定至辅助服务的顶级接口。普通应用绝不需要此权限。

OriginalText: Allows the holder to bind to the top-level interface of a text service(e.g. SpellCheckerService). Should never be needed for normal apps.
TranslatedText: 允许用户绑定至文字服务（如 SpellCheckerService）的顶级接口。普通应用绝不需要此权限。

OriginalText: Allows the holder to bind to the top-level interface of a Vpn service. Should never be needed for normal apps.
TranslatedText: 允许用户绑定到 VPN 服务的顶级接口。普通应用绝不需要此权限。

OriginalText: Allows the holder to bind to the top-level interface of a wallpaper. Should never be needed for normal apps.
TranslatedText: 允许用户绑定到壁纸的顶级接口。普通应用绝不需要此权限。
绑定到窗口小部件服务

OriginalText: Allows the holder to bind to the top-level interface of a widget service. Should never be needed for normal apps.
TranslatedText: 允许用户绑定到窗口小部件服务的顶级接口。普通应用绝不需要此权限。

OriginalText: Allows the holder to send intents to a device administrator. Should never be needed for normal apps.
TranslatedText: 允许用户将意向发送给设备管理员。普通应用绝不需要此权限。

OriginalText: Allows the app to change the rotation of the screen at any time. Should never be needed for normal apps.
TranslatedText: 允许应用随时更改屏幕的旋转状态。普通应用绝不需要此权限。

OriginalText: Allows the app to change the mouse or trackpad pointer speed at any time. Should never be needed for normal apps.
TranslatedText: 允许应用随时更改鼠标或触控板指针速度。普通应用绝不需要此权限。

OriginalText: Allows the app to change the keyboard layout. Should never be needed for normal apps.
TranslatedText: 允许应用更改键盘布局。普通应用绝不需要此权限。
向应用发送 Linux 信号

OriginalText: Allows the app to request that the supplied signal be sent to all persistent processes.
TranslatedText: 允许应用请求将提供的信号发送给所有持续的进程。

OriginalText: Allows the app to make parts of itself persistent in memory. This can limit memory available to other apps slowing down the phone.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用在内存中持续保留其自身的某些组件。这会限制其他应用可用的内存，从而减缓手机运行速度。

OriginalText: Allows the app to delete Android packages. Malicious apps may use this to delete important apps.
TranslatedText: 允许应用删除 Android 程序包。恶意应用可能借此删除重要的应用。

OriginalText: Allows the app to clear user data.
TranslatedText: 允许应用清除用户数据。

OriginalText: Allows the app to delete cache files.
TranslatedText: 允许应用删除缓存文件。

OriginalText: Allows the app to retrieve its code, data, and cache sizes
TranslatedText: 允许应用检索其代码、数据和缓存大小

OriginalText: Allows the app to install new or updated Android packages. Malicious apps may use this to add new apps with arbitrarily powerful permissions.
TranslatedText: 允许应用安装新的或更新的 Andr​​oid 程序包。恶意应用可能借此添加具有任意权限的新应用。
删除所有应用缓存数据

OriginalText: Allows the app to free phone storage by deleting files in app cache directory. Access is very restricted usually to system process.
TranslatedText: 允许应用删除应用缓存目录中的文件，从而释放手机的存储空间。对系统进程的访问权限通常受到很大的限制。

OriginalText: Allows the app to move app resources from internal to external media and vice versa.
TranslatedText: 允许应用在内部与外部媒体之间移动应用资源。

OriginalText: Allows an application to override the power key
TranslatedText: 允许应用程序完全掌控电源键。

OriginalText: Allows the app to read from the system's various log files. This allows it to discover general information about what you are doing with the phone
TranslatedText: potentially including personal or private information.""
column5: 允许应用从系统的各个日志文件中读取信息。这样，应用就可以发现关于您手机使用情况的一般信息，其中可能包含个人信息或隐私信息。

OriginalText: use any media decoder for playback
TranslatedText: 使用任何媒体解码器进行播放

OriginalText: Allows the app to use any installed media decoder to decode for playback.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用使用任何已安装的媒体解码器进行解码，以便播放媒体。

OriginalText: read/write to resources owned by diag
TranslatedText: 读取/写入诊断所拥有的资源

OriginalText: Allows the app to read and write to any resource owned by the diag group; for example, files in /dev. This could potentially affect system stability and security. This should be ONLY be used for hardware-specific diagnostics by the manufacturer or operator.
TranslatedText: 允许应用读取/写入诊断组拥有的所有资源（例如 /dev 中的文件）。这可能会影响系统的稳定性和安全性。此权限仅供制造商或运营商诊断硬件方面的问题时使用。

OriginalText: Allows the app to change whether a component of another app is enabled or not. Malicious apps may use this to disable important phone capabilities. Care must be used with this permission, as it is possible to get app components into an unusable, inconsistent, or unstable state.
TranslatedText: 允许应用启用或停用其他应用的组件。恶意应用可能借此停用重要的手机功能。请务必谨慎使用此权限，因为这可能导致某些应用组件进入无法使用、不一致或不稳定的状态。

OriginalText: Allows an application to grant or revoke specific permissions for it or other applications. Malicious applications may use this to access features you have not granted them.
TranslatedText: 允许应用针对自身或其他应用授予或撤消特定权限。恶意应用可能会借此访问您未授权它们访问的功能。

OriginalText: Allows the app to modify your preferred apps. Malicious apps may silently change the apps that are run, spoofing your existing apps to collect private data from you.
TranslatedText: 允许应用修改您的首选应用。恶意应用可能会在后台更改运行的应用，欺骗您现有的应用，以收集您的私人数据。

OriginalText: Allows the app to modify the system's settings data. Malicious apps may corrupt your system's configuration.""
TranslatedText: 允许应用修改系统的设置数据。恶意应用可能会破坏您的系统配置。

OriginalText: Allows the app to modify the system's secure settings data. Not for use by normal apps.""
TranslatedText: 允许应用修改系统的安全设置数据。普通应用不能使用此权限。
修改 Google 服务地图

OriginalText: Allows the app to modify the Google services map. Not for use by normal apps.
TranslatedText: 允许应用修改 Google 服务地图。普通应用不能使用此权限。

OriginalText: Allows the app to have itself started as soon as the system has finished booting. This can make it take longer to start the phone and allow the app to slow down the overall phone by always running.
TranslatedText: 允许应用在系统完成引导后立即自动启动。这样可能会延长手机的启动时间，并允许应用始终运行，从而导致手机总体运行速度减慢。

OriginalText: Allows the app to send sticky broadcasts, which remain after the broadcast ends. Excessive use may make the phone slow or unstable by causing it to use too much memory.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用发送持久广播消息，此类消息在广播结束后仍会保留。过度使用可能会导致手机使用过多内存，从而降低其速度或稳定性。

OriginalText: Allows the app to read data about your contacts stored on your phone
TranslatedText: including the frequency with which you've called
column5: emailed
column6: or communicated in other ways with specific individuals. This permission allows apps to save your contact data
column7: and malicious apps may share contact data without your knowledge.""
column8: 允许该应用读取您手机上存储的联系人的相关数据，包括您通过打电话、发送电子邮件或以其他方式与特定个人通信的频率。此权限可让应用保存您的联系人数据，而恶意应用可能会在您不知情的情况下分享联系人数据。

OriginalText: Allows the app to modify the data about your contacts stored on your phone
TranslatedText: including the frequency with which you've called
column5: emailed
column6: or communicated in other ways with specific contacts. This permission allows apps to delete contact data.""
column7: 允许该应用修改您手机上存储的联系人的相关数据，包括您通过打电话、发送电子邮件或以其他方式与特定联系人通信的频率。此权限可让应用删除联系人数据。

OriginalText: Allows the app to read your phone's call log
TranslatedText: including data about incoming and outgoing calls. This permission allows apps to save your call log data
column5: and malicious apps may share call log data without your knowledge.""
column6: 允许该应用读取手机的通话记录，包括有关来电和外拨电话的数据。此权限可让应用保存您的通话记录数据，而恶意应用可能会在您不知情的情况下分享通话记录数据。

OriginalText: Allows the app to modify your phone's call log
TranslatedText: including data about incoming and outgoing calls. Malicious apps may use this to erase or modify your call log.""
column5: 允许该应用修改手机的通话记录，包括有关来电和外拨电话的数据。恶意应用可能会借此清除或修改您的通话记录。

OriginalText: Allows the app to read personal profile information stored on your device, such as your name and contact information. This means the app can identify you and may send your profile information to others.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用读取您设备上存储的个人资料信息，例如您的姓名和联系信息。这意味着该应用可以识别您的身份，并可能将您的个人资料信息发送给他人。

OriginalText: Allows the app to change or add to personal profile information stored on your device, such as your name and contact information. This means the app can identify you and may send your profile information to others.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用更改或添加您设备上存储的个人资料信息，例如您的姓名和联系信息。这意味着该应用可以识别您的身份，并可能将您的个人资料信息发送给他人。

OriginalText: Allows the app to access and sync social updates from you and your friends. Be careful when sharing information -- this allows the app to read communications between you and your friends on social networks, regardless of confidentiality. Note: this permission may not be enforced on all social networks.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用访问并同步您和朋友的社交动态信息。在分享信息时一定要小心，因为此权限可让该应用读取您与社交网络上的朋友之间的交流信息。

OriginalText: Allows the app to display social updates from your friends. Be careful when sharing information -- this allows the app to produce messages that may appear to come from a friend. Note: this permission may not be enforced on all social networks.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用显示您朋友的社交动态信息。在分享信息时一定要小心，因为此权限可让该应用冒充某个朋友编写消息。请注意：此权限可能不适用于所有社交网络。

OriginalText: read calendar events plus confidential information
TranslatedText: 读取日历活动和机密信息

OriginalText: Allows the app to read all calendar events stored on your phone, including those of friends or co-workers. This may allow the app to share or save your calendar data, regardless of confidentiality or sensitivity.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用读取您手机上存储的所有日历活动，包括朋友或同事的活动。此权限可让该应用分享或保存您的日历数据，而不论这些数据是否属于机密或敏感内容。

OriginalText: add or modify calendar events and send email to guests without owners' knowledge""
TranslatedText: 添加或修改日历活动，并在所有者不知情的情况下向邀请对象发送电子邮件

column5: change events that you can modify on your phone
column6: including those of friends or co-workers. This may allow the app to send messages that appear to come from calendar owners
column7: or modify events without the owners' knowledge.""
column8: 允许该应用添加、删除、更改您可在手机上修改的活动，包括朋友或同事的活动。此权限可让该应用冒充日历所有者发送消息，或在所有者不知情的情况下修改活动。

TranslatedText: 使用模拟地点来源进行测试

OriginalText: Create mock location sources for testing or install a new location provider. This allows the app to override the location and/or status returned by other location sources such as GPS or location providers.
TranslatedText: 创建用于测试的模拟位置源或安装新的位置提供程序。此权限可让该应用覆盖由其他位置源（如 GPS）或位置提供程序返回的位置和/或状态信息。
获取额外的位置信息提供程序命令

OriginalText: Allows the app to access extra location provider commands. This may allow the app to to interfere with the operation of the GPS or other location sources.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用访问额外的位置提供程序命令。此权限可让该应用干扰 GPS 或其他位置源的运行。

OriginalText: permission to install a location provider
TranslatedText: 允许安装位置信息提供程序

OriginalText: Create mock location sources for testing or install a new location provider. This allows the app to override the location and/or status returned by other location sources such as GPS or location providers.
TranslatedText: 创建用于测试的模拟位置源或安装新的位置提供程序。此权限可让该应用覆盖由其他位置源（如 GPS）或位置提供程序返回的位置和/或状态信息。

OriginalText: Access precise location sources such as the Global Positioning System on the phone. When location services are available and turned on, this permission allows the app to determine your precise location.
TranslatedText: 访问手机上的 GPS 等确切位置源。当位置服务可用且处于启用状态时，此权限可让该应用确定您的确切位置。

OriginalText: Access approximate location from location providers using network sources such as cell tower and Wi-Fi. When these location services are available and turned on, this permission allows the app to determine your approximate location.
TranslatedText: 访问位置提供程序根据基站和 Wi-Fi 等网络源确定的大概位置。当这些位置服务可用且处于启用状态时，此权限可让该应用确定您的大概位置。

OriginalText: Allows the app to use SurfaceFlinger low-level features.
TranslatedText: 允许应用使用 SurfaceFlinger 低级功能。

OriginalText: Allows the app to read the content of the frame buffer.
TranslatedText: 允许应用读取帧缓冲区的内容。

OriginalText: Allows the app to modify global audio settings such as volume and which speaker is used for output.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用修改全局音频设置，例如音量和用于输出的扬声器。

OriginalText: Allows the app to record audio with the microphone. This permission allows the app to record audio at any time without your confirmation.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用使用麦克风录制音频。此权限可让该应用不经您的确认即可随时录制音频。

OriginalText: Allows the app to take pictures and videos with the camera. This permission allows the app to use the camera at any time without your confirmation.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用使用相机拍摄照片和视频。此权限可让该应用随时使用相机，而无需您的确认。

OriginalText: Allows the app to disable the entire phone permanently. This is very dangerous.
TranslatedText: 允许应用永久停用整个手机，但这非常危险。

OriginalText: Allows the app to force the phone to reboot.
TranslatedText: 允许应用强行重新启动手机。
访问 SD 卡文件系统

OriginalText: Allows the app to mount and unmount filesystems for removable storage.
TranslatedText: 允许应用装载和卸载可移动存储设备的文件系统。

OriginalText: Allows the app to format removable storage.
TranslatedText: 允许应用格式化可移动存储设备。
获取有关内部存储设备的信息

OriginalText: Allows the app to get information on internal storage.
TranslatedText: 允许应用获取有关内存设备的信息。

OriginalText: Allows the app to create internal storage.
TranslatedText: 允许应用创建内存设备。

OriginalText: Allows the app to destroy internal storage.
TranslatedText: 允许应用清除内存设备。

OriginalText: Allows the app to mount/unmount internal storage.
TranslatedText: 允许应用装载/卸载内存设备。

OriginalText: Allows the app to rename internal storage.
TranslatedText: 允许应用重命名内存设备。

OriginalText: Allows the app to control the vibrator.
Allows the app to control the flashlight.
manage preferences and permissions for USB devices
TranslatedText: 管理 USB 设备的偏好设置和权限

OriginalText: Allows the app to manage preferences and permissions for USB devices.
TranslatedText: 允许应用管理针对 USB 设备的偏好设置和权限。

OriginalText: Allows access to the kernel MTP driver to implement the MTP USB protocol.
TranslatedText: 允许访问内核 MTP 驱动程序，以便应用 MTP USB 协议。

OriginalText: Allows the app to control various peripherals for the purpose of hardware testing.
TranslatedText: 允许应用控制各种外围设备以进行硬件测试。

OriginalText: Allows the app to call phone numbers without your intervention. This may result in unexpected charges or calls. Note that this doesn't allow the app to call emergency numbers. Malicious apps may cost you money by making calls without your confirmation.""
TranslatedText: 允许该应用在您未执行操作的情况下拨打电话号码。此权限可能会导致意外收费或呼叫。请注意，此权限不允许该应用拨打紧急电话号码。恶意应用可通过拨打电话产生相关费用，而无需您的确认。
直接呼叫任何电话号码

OriginalText: Allows the app to call any phone number, including emergency numbers, without your intervention. Malicious apps may place unnecessary and illegal calls to emergency services.
TranslatedText: 允许应用在没有您干预的情况下拨打任何电话号码，包括紧急呼救号码。恶意应用可能会多余以及非法地拨打紧急服务的号码。
直接启动 CDMA 电话设置

OriginalText: Allows the app to start CDMA provisioning. Malicious apps may unnecessarily start CDMA provisioning.
TranslatedText: 允许应用启动 CDMA 配置。恶意应用可能会无端启动 CDMA 配置。

OriginalText: Allows the app to enable/disable location update notifications from the radio. Not for use by normal apps.
TranslatedText: 允许应用启用/停用来自无线装置的位置更新通知。普通应用不能使用此权限。

OriginalText: Allows the app read/write access to properties uploaded by the checkin service. Not for use by normal apps.
TranslatedText: 允许应用对登记服务上传的属性拥有读取/写入权限。普通应用不能使用此权限。

OriginalText: Allows the app to tell the system which widgets can be used by which app. An app with this permission can give access to personal data to other apps. Not for use by normal apps.
TranslatedText: 允许应用告知系统哪些窗口小部件可供哪个应用使用。拥有此权限的应用可向其他应用授予对个人资料的访问权限。普通应用不能使用此权限。

OriginalText: Allows the app to control the phone features of the device. An app with this permission can switch networks, turn the phone radio on and off and the like without ever notifying you.
TranslatedText: 允许应用控制设备的电话功能。拥有此权限的应用可在不通知您的情况下执行切换网络、开关手机无线装置等此类操作。

OriginalText: Allows the app to access the phone features of the device. This permission allows the app to determine the phone number and device IDs, whether a call is active, and the remote number connected by a call.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用访问设备的电话功能。此权限可让该应用确定本机号码和设备 ID、是否正处于通话状态以及拨打的号码。

OriginalText: Allows the app to prevent the phone from going to sleep.
TranslatedText: 允许应用阻止手机进入休眠状态。

OriginalText: Allows the app to turn the phone on or off.
TranslatedText: 允许应用打开或关闭手机。
在出厂测试模式下运行

OriginalText: Run as a low-level manufacturer test, allowing complete access to the phone hardware. Only available when a phone is running in manufacturer test mode.
TranslatedText: 作为一项低级制造商测试来运行，从而允许对手机硬件进行完全访问。此权限仅当手机在制造商测试模式下运行时才可用。。

OriginalText: Allows the app to set the system wallpaper.
TranslatedText: 允许应用设置系统壁纸。

OriginalText: Allows the app to set the system wallpaper size hints.
TranslatedText: 允许应用设置有关系统壁纸大小的提示。
将系统恢复为出厂设置

OriginalText: Allows the app to completely reset the system to its factory settings, erasing all data, configuration, and installed apps.
TranslatedText: 允许应用将系统完全重置为其出厂设置，这会清除所有数据、配置和已安装的应用。

OriginalText: Allows the app to change the phone's clock time.""
TranslatedText: 允许应用更改手机的时间。

OriginalText: Allows the app to change the phone's time zone.""
TranslatedText: 允许应用更改手机的时区。

OriginalText: Allows the app to make calls to AccountAuthenticators.
Allows the app to get the list of accounts known by the phone. This may include any accounts created by applications you have installed.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用获取手机已知的帐户列表，其中可能包括由已安装的应用创建的所有帐户。

OriginalText: Allows the app to use the account authenticator capabilities of the AccountManager, including creating accounts and getting and setting their passwords.
TranslatedText: 允许应用使用 AccountManager 的帐户身份验证程序功能，包括创建帐户以及获取和设置其密码。

OriginalText: Allows the app to perform operations like adding and removing accounts, and deleting their password.
TranslatedText: 允许应用执行添加帐户、删除帐户、删除帐户密码等操作。

OriginalText: Allows the app to request authentication tokens.
TranslatedText: 允许应用请求身份验证令牌。

OriginalText: Allows the app to view information about network connections such as which networks exist and are connected.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用查看网络连接的相关信息，例如存在和连接的网络。

OriginalText: Allows the app to create network sockets and use custom network protocols. The browser and other applications provide means to send data to the internet, so this permission is not required to send data to the internet.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用创建网络套接字和使用自定义网络协议。浏览器和其他某些应用提供了向互联网发送数据的途径，因此应用无需该权限即可向互联网发送数据。
更改/拦截网络设置和流量

OriginalText: Allows the app to change network settings and to intercept and inspect all network traffic, for example to change the proxy and port of any APN. Malicious apps may monitor, redirect, or modify network packets without your knowledge.
TranslatedText: 允许应用更改网络设置，并拦截和检查所有网络流量，例如更改任意 APN 的代理和端口。恶意应用可能会在您不知情的情况下监视、重定向或修改网络数据包。

OriginalText: Allows the app to change the state of network connectivity.
TranslatedText: 允许应用更改网络连接的状态。

OriginalText: Allows the app to change the state of tethered network connectivity.
TranslatedText: 允许应用更改绑定网络连接的状态。
更改后台数据使用设置

OriginalText: Allows the app to change the background data usage setting.
TranslatedText: 允许应用更改后台数据使用设置。

OriginalText: Allows the app to view information about Wi-Fi networking, such as whether Wi-Fi is enabled and name of connected Wi-Fi devices.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用查看 Wi-Fi 网络的相关信息，例如是否启用了 Wi-Fi 以及连接的 Wi-Fi 设备的名称。
连接 Wi-Fi 和断开连接

OriginalText: Allows the app to connect to and disconnect from Wi-Fi access points and to make changes to device configuration for Wi-Fi networks.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用与 Wi-Fi 接入点建立和断开连接，以及更改 Wi-Fi 网络的设备配置。
允许接收 Wi-Fi 多播

OriginalText: Allows the app to receive packets sent to all devices on a Wi-Fi network using multicast addresses, not just your phone. It uses more power than the non-multicast mode.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用使用多播地址接收发送到 Wi-Fi 网络上所有设备（而不仅仅是您的手机）的数据包。该操作的耗电量比非多播模式要大。

OriginalText: Allows the app to configure the local Bluetooth phone, and to discover and pair with remote devices.
TranslatedText: 允许应用配置本地蓝牙手机，以及发现远程设备并进行配对。

OriginalText: Allows the app to determine whether WiMAX is enabled and information about any WiMAX networks that are connected.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用确定是否启用了 WiMAX 以及连接的任何 WiMAX 网络的相关信息。

OriginalText: Allows the app to connect the phone to and disconnect the phone from WiMAX networks.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用建立和断开手机与 WiMAX 网络之间的连接。

OriginalText: Allows the app to view the configuration of the Bluetooth on the phone, and to make and accept connections with paired devices.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用查看手机上的蓝牙配置，以及建立和接受与配对设备的连接。

OriginalText: Allows the app to communicate with Near Field Communication (NFC) tags, cards, and readers.
TranslatedText: 允许应用与近距离无线通信 (NFC) 标记、卡和阅读器进行通信。

OriginalText: Allows the app to disable the keylock and any associated password security. For example, the phone disables the keylock when receiving an incoming phone call, then re-enables the keylock when the call is finished.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用停用键锁以及任何关联的密码安全措施。例如，让手机在接听来电时停用键锁，在通话结束后重新启用键锁。

OriginalText: Allows the app to read the sync settings for an account. For example, this can determine whether the People app is synced with an account.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用读取某个帐户的同步设置。例如，此权限可确定“联系人”应用是否与某个帐户同步。

OriginalText: Allows an app to modify the sync settings for an account. For example, this can be used to enable sync of the People app with an account.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用修改某个帐户的同步设置。例如，此权限可用于在“联系人”应用与某个帐户之间启用同步。

OriginalText: Allows an app to read the sync stats for an account, including the history of sync events and how much data is synced.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用读取某个帐户的同步统计信息，包括同步活动历史记录和同步数据量。

OriginalText: Allows the app to get details about the currently synced feeds.
TranslatedText: 允许应用获取有关当前同步的 Feed 的详情。

OriginalText: Allows the app to modify your currently synced feeds. Malicious apps may change your synced feeds.
TranslatedText: 允许应用修改您当前同步的 Feed。恶意应用可能会更改您的同步 Feed。

OriginalText: read terms you added to the dictionary
TranslatedText: 读取您添加到词典的字词

OriginalText: Allows the app to read all words, names and phrases that the user may have stored in the user dictionary.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用读取用户可能已在用户词典中存储的所有字词、名称和词组。

OriginalText: Allows the app to write new words into the user dictionary.
TranslatedText: 允许应用向用户词典中写入新词。
测试对受保护存储空间的访问权限

OriginalText: Allows the app to test a permission for the SD card that will be available on future devices.
TranslatedText: 允许该应用测试将对以后的设备开放的 SD 卡权限。

OriginalText: modify or delete the contents of your SD card
TranslatedText: 修改或删除您的 SD 卡中的内容

OriginalText: Allows the app to write to the SD card.
TranslatedText: 允许应用写入 SD 卡。

OriginalText: Ghost mode hides the Superuser icon from the launcher. The icon will be hidden the next time the launcher is restarted. Once the icon is hidden you can access Superuser by dialing a secret code in the dialer. The default secret code is *#*#787378737#*#* (*#*#superuser#*#*)

FieldName: you probably shouldn't enable Ghost mode.

OriginalText: This updater is incapable of updating your su binary since it is installed in /sbin. This is not an error in the updater, it is an error on the behalf of your ROM or kernel developer. You can continue to use Superuser with your outdated binary.

OriginalText: This updater cannot update the su binary on phones that have some kind of write protection on the system partition like S-ON. You can continue to use Superuser with your outdated binary, or update su with ROM Manager.
TranslatedText: 更新程序无法在 system 分区有写保护（比如 S-ON）的设备上更新 su 二进制可执行文件。 您可以保留旧版 su 继续使用超级用户，或者使用 ROM Manager 更新 su 二进制可执行文件。
